OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill stay dry and mainly cloudy with
OL,7,Fthe odd bright spell. Overnight will
OL,8,Fremain mostly dry but with perhaps a
OL,9,Flight shower later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA cloudy start, perhaps a
OL,12,Flight shower or two over Orkney, then
OL,13,Fbrightening up from the north with
OL,14,Fsome sunny spells developing in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Fresh northerly winds,
OL,16,Ffeeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
