OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSome
OL,6,Fsunny spells on Sunday, then clouding
OL,7,Fover later with some light rain.
OL,8,FMonday mainly dry with some sunny
OL,9,Fintervals. Then cloudier on Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith some patchy drizzle.
